```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(pander)
library(dplyr)
library(readr)
```


```{r}
bendata <- read_csv("rbdata.csv")
```

```{r}
plot(y~x8,bendata)
```
```{r}
benlm <- lm(y ~ x9:x10:(
                     x8 + I(x8^3) + x8:x1 + I(x8^3):x2 + I(x8^5):x6 + I(x8^-1):x3 + x8:x4 + I(x8^3):x5 + I(x8^5):x6:x7),data=bendata)

summary(benlm)
```

```{r}
zachlm <- lm(y^2 ~ I(x8^2) + I(x1) + I(x1):I(x8^2) + x7 + x9:x7:x8 + x7:I(x8^2),data=bendata)
summary(zachlm)
```
